<section id="guides">
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10562" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW"><link href="text/shared/01/guides.xhp">Guides</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3146313" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">Specifies the display options for guides on the screen.</paragraph>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105AA" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW"><link href="text/shared/00/00000403.xhp#guides"><embedvar href="text/shared/00/00000004.xhp#wie"/></link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1057B" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Display Guides</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1057F" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Displays or hides guides that you can use to align objects on a page.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10582" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Snap to Guides</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10586" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Automatically aligns objects to vertical and horizontal guides. To override this feature, hold down the <switchinline select="sys"><caseinline select="MAC">Control key 
</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl key when you drag an object.</defaultinline></switchinline>.<comment>UFI: test it! copied from shared\01\grid.xhp</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105C6" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Guides to Front</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105CA" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Displays the guides in front of the object on the page.</paragraph>
